Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:30.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:36.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:44.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:51.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:01:00.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:05.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:10.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:15.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:23.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:27.30,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,39 星之继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你 对娜蒂亚开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 你狠得下心 对娜蒂亚开枪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使是用你爱的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚公主的意识 已经唤不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱持着宽大的慈悲心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再给你一次活下去的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你愿意以 亚特兰提斯人之王的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,协助我们将愚蠢的人类 带往正途吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,答案还是跟13年前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还没清醒过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劝你别太小看人类 石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类并不如你所想的那么愚昧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒不认为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像那名少年 就无法对娜蒂亚开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他应该毫不犹豫 扣下扳机才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你错了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那才是人类的善良之处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是他们的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 那是不需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是时候让你消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前先让你听听 你亲生儿子的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我以友人身分送给你的 最后一个礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彼那西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吾乃新亚特兰提斯帝国皇帝 尼欧·伊肯·艾皮法尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼 难不成你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你儿子现在不过是我的 扯线木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼欧 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对尼莫开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被自己的孩子杀死 是什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你将会死在自己孩子的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我这位好友的一点心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新鹦鹉螺号 听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新鹦鹉螺号 听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 这里是鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长 你平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晓得我的位置吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 追踪得到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将座标往左偏移60 发射电子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那样太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,运气好的话就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再这样下去只会坐以待毙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请发射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然船长就要被杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何啊？尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成果很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我们新亚特兰提斯的 科学结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是…科学？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他的肉体早在13年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就被尼莫 和巴别塔一起四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多亏有我藉由科学的力量救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此让你的儿子多活了13年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我觉得自己应该受人感谢 而不是怨恨才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到会遭到主炮直接攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶的遗迹战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然刻意瞄准尼欧的控制装置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父王？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成…不可能会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼欧的意识 明明就已经彻底消除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在竟然又恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这简直是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除非破坏控制装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,否则娜蒂亚不可能清醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你忘了是谁将我的身体 改造成金属的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彼那西斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼欧 你不过是个机器娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,电源一断只能落得这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇迹就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在你连一根手指头都动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就直接下黄泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如此不合乎科学的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道人的意志力 真的足以超越科学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彼那西斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真希望我也能跟人类一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是愚蠢家伙的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闹剧就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再这样下去会直接冲入大气圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是红色诺亚 以这样的角度根本…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法 只好硬干了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今尼欧皇帝已经逝世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水的继承人就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明是你杀死他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为他已经没有用处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以就处分掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚公主 请你将蔚蓝之水复原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并将这艘船导回正确轨道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不在乎他们的死活吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我身为蔚蓝之水的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,决定要毁灭这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不需要担心我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新鹦鹉螺号一定会来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时候我们就一起回地球去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他还是一样那么勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惜太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然不知珍惜自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愚蠢的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以为凡事都能随意掌控的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是人心可不像机械一样 能随你任意操弄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我爸爸和哥哥 都不惜为了自己的信念牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也继承他们的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会让你称心如意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我勉强饶了她一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下你愿意让蔚蓝之水复原了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是采取合理的手段 以求达到目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧 娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你就看看心上人的尸体 再来后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遗迹战舰！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强！强！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把这个拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向两颗蔚蓝之水许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水一定会回应你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是如果没有蔚蓝之水 你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你是个女人 就该优先救自己心上人的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女人就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水将会永远失去光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望之光…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能在那道光芒中存活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有亚特兰提斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我为什么会变成盐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个世上的亚特兰提斯人 现在只剩下两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涅墨西斯·拉·阿尔果 你是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我至今所做的一切不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟娜蒂亚两个外星人 又能做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个星球已经是人类的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是谁将我从沉睡中唤醒的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是娜蒂亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你…请你救救强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是他的生命已经走到尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是尼莫船长说你可以救他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你 救救强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是这么一来 你将会失去蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去你因为身为亚特兰提斯人 而被赋予的一切力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是放弃成为神的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我根本不需要那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你…请你救救强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:18:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这颗石头是 亚特兰提斯人灵魂的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就将我们的生命献给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没事 全员立刻登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷稳定器受损
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎输出动力降至0.2%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 根本动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 没救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以说泄气话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们一定要活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:20:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与新鹦鹉螺号连接电源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始填充能源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离启动可能时间还有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会用新鹦鹉螺号破坏发射口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为你们开出一条活路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:21:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我这个父亲能为你做的 就只有这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要 我也要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要跟爸爸一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你体谅他的苦心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孩子们就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 梅蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后的事就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不论遇到什么困难
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你都要活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们在太空船里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.65,0:23:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太空船？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 我们即将返回你的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说错了 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我们的故乡才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是你出生的星球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我一样都是地球人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉许了什么愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.85,0:23:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望桑森还有大家 能早点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.43,0:24:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望以后不要再发生同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(全剧终)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.86,0:24:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个故事到此全部结束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.30,0:24:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来向各位报告一些 之后的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.47,0:24:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从那之后已经过了12年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.47,0:24:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新的鹦鹉螺号 沉入了日本海沟深处
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.47,0:24:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船员们现在都过着各自的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.95,0:24:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾科哥哥和护士姐姐 在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.75,0:24:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉则是听说 一心一意将孩子抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.55,0:25:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强与娜蒂亚终于在5年前结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.06,0:25:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前定居勒阿弗尔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.23,0:25:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说强现在也还是一样 和他的姑丈埋头发明
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.97,0:25:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,害得娜蒂亚与姑姑 总是有发不完的牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.04,0:25:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚虽然已经当了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.91,0:25:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却还是一样不肯吃鱼跟肉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.21,0:25:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.45,0:25:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝至今好像还是一个人 享受着自由自在的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.32,0:25:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她会永远追求 属于自己的爱情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.52,0:25:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森开了间汽车公司
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.36,0:25:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成了我们之中最有钱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.13,0:25:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『我就只差一位漂亮老婆了』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.20,0:25:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上次见面时他这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.24,0:25:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿听说回到英国 乖乖继承家业
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.41,0:25:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来他真的是位伯爵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.78,0:26:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森过得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.88,0:26:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.82,0:26:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他现在是我 玛莉·安·雷温佛洛伊的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.69,0:26:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而明年我就要跟娜蒂亚一样 当妈妈了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.33,0:26:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我的梦想就是在星期天 全家人一起到附近的公园散步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.61,0:26:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 后会有期啰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.58,0:26:43.51,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.59,0:26:48.58,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.66,0:26:53.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.07,0:27:01.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.91,0:27:11.98,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.05,0:27:20.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.93,0:27:25.02,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.10,0:27:29.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.80,0:27:39.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.69,0:27:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里终于完结了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.39,0:27:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这一年看似漫长 其实一贬眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.23,0:27:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.99,0:27:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.83,0:28:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这一年从世界各地 寄来的插画与明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.57,0:28:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然高达10万2318封喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.64,0:28:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.80,0:28:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来有这么多人 都在为我们加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.24,0:28:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让人好开心喔\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.08,0:28:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.91,0:28:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这一年与我们 一同经历了这场冒险之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.11,0:28:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及来信鼓励我们 与这部作品工作人员的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.28,0:28:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很谢谢你们\N真的很谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.82,0:28:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 后会有期啰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.56,0:28:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见啰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.69,0:28:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜拜\N拜拜
